QueryText: INFORMATION REGARDING FOR THE SOWING TIME OF POTATO(ALOO)?
KCCAns: THE SOWING TIME OF POTATO(ALOO)-FIRST SOWING-LAST WEEK OF SEP. TO MID OCT. & SECOND SOWING-FORTNIGHT OF JANUARY.

QueryText: INFORMATION  REGARDING CONTROL OF SHEATH BLIGHT IN PADDY?
KCCAns: SPRAY TILT @ 200 ML IN 200 LITERS WATER/ACRE.

QueryText: INFORMATION REGARDING FOR THE CONTROL OF BROWN LEAF SPOT  DISEASE ATTACK ON PADDY(JHONA) CROP?
KCCAns: FOR THE CONTROL OF BROWN LEAF SPOT  DISEASE ATTACK ON PADDY, SPRAY 200 ML TILT 25 EC OR FOLICUR 25 EC IN 200 LITRE WATER PER ACRE

QueryText: INFORMATION RGEARDING FOR THE CONTROL OF SHEATH BLIGHT ATTACK ON PADDY(JHONA) CROP?
KCCAns: SPRAY 200 ML TILT (PROPICONAZOL  25%) MIX IN 200 LITER WATER /ACER .
